Reviews.Title: Works well
Reviews.Author: Robert Faircloth
Reviews.Content: I have no complaints whatsoever.  The item shipped quickly and the price was great. I needed all 66 feet for my installation on board a yacht and there is no problem at all with signal strength or voltage at the cams at the end of the line.  Thanks to the seller for providing this item.I recommend this to others.

Reviews.Title: Product sucked!
Reviews.Author: Rashelle
Reviews.Content: The cable had problems the power cable on it. Husband not impressed. We had to modify the cable to get it to work.

Reviews.Title: CCTV cables
Reviews.Author: E. Cady
Reviews.Content: Ordered two packages and they work perfectly.  Arrived on time and in excellent condition.  Tested the cables for 24 plus hours for a burn-in without an impact on Camera performance.

Reviews.Title: A great value
Reviews.Author: snackdaddy
Reviews.Content: I bought these cables because the 50ft cables that came with my DVR camera system were just short of what i needed. They came before the scheduled delivery time. That was nice also
